<para>Hook predicate that may be define in the module <computeroutput>user</computeroutput> to intercept messages from <ref refid="classprint__message_22" kindref="compound">print_message/2</ref> <emphasis>Term</emphasis> and <emphasis>Kind</emphasis> are the same as passed to <ref refid="classprint__message_22" kindref="compound">print_message/2</ref> <emphasis>Lines</emphasis> is a list of format statements as described with <ref refid="classprint__message__lines_23" kindref="compound">print_message_lines/3</ref></para>
<para>This predicate should be defined dynamic and multifile to allow other modules defining clauses for it too </para>
